snippet.title: NervBox Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam Early Access! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2168200/NervBox/

NervBox is a VR, physics-based, multiplayer sandbox where players can experience an unparalleled level of co-op interaction and combat.

https://nervbox.com/
